00:02:12.208 --> 00:02:15.541
BUJJI THALLI

00:03:21.041 --> 00:03:23.416
Please, Raju.
Don't go fishing.

00:03:23.791 --> 00:03:24.791
I won't leave you.

00:03:25.541 --> 00:03:28.041
- Promise?
- I won't. Okay?

00:03:31.208 --> 00:03:34.500
The storm shows no signs of letting up.
Pile them up in the storage deck.

00:03:36.041 --> 00:03:38.416
You promised!
What's this?

00:03:38.500 --> 00:03:41.750
As soon as I return from fishing,
we'll get married.

00:03:42.541 --> 00:03:44.583
Daddha, the waves are getting stronger.

00:03:44.666 --> 00:03:45.916
Turn the boats around, now!

00:03:48.375 --> 00:03:51.375
If you're leaving now,
it's not just to go fishing.

00:03:51.458 --> 00:03:52.875
You're leaving me for good.

00:03:54.833 --> 00:03:57.416
Hey, Raju!
Think again!

00:04:26.375 --> 00:04:27.208
Sathya?

00:04:28.583 --> 00:04:30.125
What's this, dear?

00:04:33.708 --> 00:04:35.125
Let's go home, dear.

00:05:37.916 --> 00:05:39.541
- Dad.
- Yes, dear?

00:05:40.208 --> 00:05:41.500
Find a groom for me.

00:05:43.666 --> 00:05:44.500
What did you say?

00:05:45.083 --> 00:05:46.666
You know I think carefully
before making decisions.

00:05:57.583 --> 00:05:59.208
Not the studs, sister.
Give me the hangings.

00:06:03.708 --> 00:06:04.541
What is it?

00:06:05.458 --> 00:06:09.000
When he wasn't in the village,
I didn't care about how I looked.

00:06:09.958 --> 00:06:13.250
When he was around,
I wanted to look the way he liked.

00:06:14.708 --> 00:06:16.708
But now that
he's no longer in my life,

00:06:17.125 --> 00:06:19.083
I feel like looking my absolute best.

00:06:19.166 --> 00:06:20.291
Are you angry with him?

00:06:21.208 --> 00:06:24.041
When there's no love,
how can there be any anger, sister?

00:06:26.791 --> 00:06:29.583
{\an8}So, what does
the groom do for a living?

00:06:30.041 --> 00:06:31.041
The name is Murali.

00:06:31.625 --> 00:06:33.375
Do you know
there's a finance company in our village?

00:06:33.750 --> 00:06:35.625
He's working as
a recovery agent for them.

00:06:37.375 --> 00:06:40.750
As a recovery agent,
he collects monthly installments.

00:06:41.083 --> 00:06:42.708
If not, he confiscates the goods.

00:06:43.666 --> 00:06:45.375
{\an8}What's all this
fuss about recovery

00:06:45.458 --> 00:06:46.500
when we're heading
for a wedding proposal?

00:06:46.583 --> 00:06:48.875
{\an8}- First, hold on to it tight.
- Keep going.

00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:53.333
What is it?
What are we waiting for?

00:06:53.416 --> 00:06:54.500
Please call the girl quickly.

00:06:54.625 --> 00:06:55.791
I can't stay patient any longer.

00:06:56.583 --> 00:06:58.958
I have a few recoveries
to complete. I need to go.

00:07:05.583 --> 00:07:06.416
Wow!

00:07:06.958 --> 00:07:08.000
She's so beautiful!

00:07:10.625 --> 00:07:12.000
Does my face deserve
such a good-looking girl?

00:07:13.041 --> 00:07:15.333
She must have been
pressured into this meeting.

00:07:16.208 --> 00:07:17.458
This won't work out anyway.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:18.875
Please sit.

00:07:19.541 --> 00:07:20.416
Sit down.

00:07:20.958 --> 00:07:24.541
If you need some privacy,
go over there. We're okay with it.

00:07:24.625 --> 00:07:25.875
- Dad.
- You have something to say?

00:07:26.166 --> 00:07:27.708
- I agree to this wedding.
- Sathya!

00:07:31.125 --> 00:07:31.958
That's good!

00:07:32.041 --> 00:07:35.333
Clearly, the groom is double okay.
Look at him gape.

00:07:36.416 --> 00:07:37.750
Let's hurry up then, brother-in-law.

00:07:37.833 --> 00:07:40.833
Hand us your daughter's horoscope
and we'll fix an auspicious date.

00:07:40.916 --> 00:07:41.791
Sure.

00:07:42.625 --> 00:07:44.125
Hey! What are you saying, Dad?

00:07:44.208 --> 00:07:45.166
Have you seen me?

00:07:45.916 --> 00:07:47.958
In seven generations of our family line,

00:07:48.125 --> 00:07:49.875
has there ever been a girl
as beautiful as her?

00:07:51.208 --> 00:07:54.875
The horoscopes must have matched,
that's why the girl agreed.

00:07:57.666 --> 00:08:00.125
No matching the horoscopes, etc.
Let's fix the wedding straight away!

00:08:22.541 --> 00:08:24.625
Isn't your Shiva mighty?

00:08:25.375 --> 00:08:28.583
Is it true your heart's desire gets
fulfilled the moment you wish for it?

00:08:30.958 --> 00:08:31.833
Hail Lord Shiva!

00:08:32.625 --> 00:08:33.666
Why did you want to meet?

00:08:34.500 --> 00:08:35.750
I need to tell you something.

00:08:36.208 --> 00:08:38.208
Sure. Go ahead.
Just say it.

00:08:39.791 --> 00:08:40.750
His name is Raju.

00:08:45.041 --> 00:08:45.916
There you go!

00:08:46.500 --> 00:08:49.208
I was wondering how everything
surprisingly fell into place!

00:08:49.291 --> 00:08:52.416
You agreed to the wedding
and got me flying into heaven.

00:08:52.958 --> 00:08:55.416
With just a word "Raju,"
you brought me down like that.

00:08:55.500 --> 00:08:57.083
But I will marry you.

00:08:59.666 --> 00:09:00.750
What are you saying?

00:09:01.208 --> 00:09:02.708
Please be clear.

00:09:04.208 --> 00:09:05.916
For you to understand…

00:09:07.333 --> 00:09:08.791
I'll have to elaborate.

00:09:12.916 --> 00:09:15.250
{\an8}As wages are high,
our men travel 2000 kilometers

00:09:15.333 --> 00:09:17.958
from our village, D. Matchilesam,
to the Gujarat port

00:09:18.041 --> 00:09:20.291
on contracts to catch fish
for nine months.

00:09:21.583 --> 00:09:23.916
After one month of fishing,
they reach the port

00:09:24.333 --> 00:09:27.375
{\an8}and hand over the lot to the owner
before returning to the sea.

00:09:28.541 --> 00:09:30.125
During this one month at sea,

00:09:30.208 --> 00:09:31.750
they won't even have
proper network connectivity.

00:09:34.208 --> 00:09:36.000
Alright, go ahead.
Check this out, guys.

00:09:36.083 --> 00:09:37.833
For this fishing season,
he is the Thandel.

00:09:37.916 --> 00:09:38.750
Daddha.

00:09:42.541 --> 00:09:43.416
What happened?

00:09:45.333 --> 00:09:46.875
Oh my God, they caught us!

00:09:49.500 --> 00:09:50.625
We're dead.

00:09:51.125 --> 00:09:52.500
The recovery guys are coming.

00:09:52.833 --> 00:09:55.750
Here comes the nasty gang to loot us!

00:09:57.000 --> 00:10:00.083
We either have to hand over the stock
or part with 50,000 rupees.

00:10:00.166 --> 00:10:02.041
- We can't escape this time.
- Just wait.

00:10:02.125 --> 00:10:03.000
Hey, Raju!

00:10:05.166 --> 00:10:06.625
He's in his own world.

00:10:06.875 --> 00:10:08.958
{\an8}He is waiting for Sathya's call!

00:10:11.958 --> 00:10:13.833
{\an8}He is totally lost in his mobile.

00:10:13.916 --> 00:10:16.125
{\an8}Why would he care about
the stuff on the boat?

00:11:05.625 --> 00:11:06.500
Come on, have it.

00:11:07.166 --> 00:11:08.000
Hey!

00:11:09.125 --> 00:11:11.375
His phone is out of coverage. Not yours.

00:11:11.458 --> 00:11:12.458
Don't worry.

00:11:12.541 --> 00:11:13.833
He'll call you anyway.

00:11:44.416 --> 00:11:46.458
- Brother! Brother!
- Brother! Brother!

00:11:46.541 --> 00:11:50.750
- Please wait, brother.
- Please, brother.

00:11:50.916 --> 00:11:52.916
Give me the money,
or part with the load.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:54.250
This is our final hunt, brother.

00:11:54.500 --> 00:11:56.541
- These are just boys. Please leave them.
- Hey!

00:11:57.375 --> 00:11:58.250
Get the load!

00:11:58.333 --> 00:12:00.750
- Brother! Please leave us this one time.
- Please, brother.

00:12:00.833 --> 00:12:02.791
- Please, brother. Just once…
- Just wait.

00:12:05.708 --> 00:12:08.625
- No, brother.
- Brother, wait!

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:27.875
My precious.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:32.375
My precious!

00:12:42.375 --> 00:12:43.250
My precious?

00:12:46.458 --> 00:12:47.375
My precious?

00:12:48.500 --> 00:12:49.375
Raju!

00:12:49.750 --> 00:12:51.083
My…

00:12:52.375 --> 00:12:53.291
Raju!

00:12:55.833 --> 00:12:57.541
- Raju!
- Hey! You…

00:12:59.583 --> 00:13:01.750
{\an8}Raju?

00:13:06.958 --> 00:13:08.666
Hey, Raju.

00:13:14.791 --> 00:13:15.708
My precious!

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:18.375
Hey, Raju.

00:13:19.166 --> 00:13:20.583
Tell me. What's up?

00:13:20.666 --> 00:13:24.041
What's this, Raju? You called after
so long and won't even speak.

00:13:25.625 --> 00:13:27.708
The signal tower is troubling me.

00:13:28.750 --> 00:13:31.250
- So, I'm setting it up.
- What?

00:13:32.583 --> 00:13:35.000
- Setting up?
- Yes, my precious.

00:13:45.041 --> 00:13:47.791
How dare you touch my Bhavani?
You scoundrel!

00:13:52.250 --> 00:13:53.708
What's wrong, Raju?

00:13:56.333 --> 00:13:57.416
Can't you wait to die?

00:14:02.791 --> 00:14:06.208
More than the unstable signal,
it's you troubling me without talking.

00:14:11.041 --> 00:14:11.916
Raju!

00:14:12.083 --> 00:14:12.958
Raju!

00:14:17.833 --> 00:14:20.583
Please be on the line for a minute, dear.
Without speaking.

00:14:25.875 --> 00:14:28.083
Steer the boat to the jetty, Daddha.

00:14:35.208 --> 00:14:36.458
Let's rock this show!

00:15:06.083 --> 00:15:08.458
Daddha, forget a rupee,

00:15:08.833 --> 00:15:11.833
not even a little fish
must leave this boat.

00:15:21.791 --> 00:15:23.000
After a month's fishing,

00:15:23.083 --> 00:15:25.625
this is the first time
we're hearing his voice.

00:15:26.958 --> 00:15:30.583
I'd spend a month
just to hear him speak this one day.

00:15:32.916 --> 00:15:33.833
My precious one.

00:15:34.375 --> 00:15:38.083
It's so refreshing to have
a hot water bath.

00:15:38.833 --> 00:15:40.458
Raju, tell me something.

00:15:40.833 --> 00:15:42.583
Do you like taking a hot water bath

00:15:42.708 --> 00:15:44.041
or spending time with me?

00:15:44.125 --> 00:15:46.875
I'd enjoy it even more
if you were the one bathing me.

00:15:46.958 --> 00:15:47.833
Gosh!

00:15:49.166 --> 00:15:51.083
What are you saying, Raju?

00:15:51.541 --> 00:15:52.416
If Dad hears…

00:16:11.833 --> 00:16:16.041
Despite the countless distances
We've traveled together

00:16:16.125 --> 00:16:18.625
I'm never tired of this journey

00:16:20.166 --> 00:16:24.291
Despite the countless shores
That lie between us

00:16:24.375 --> 00:16:26.958
They are no obstacles at all

00:16:28.333 --> 00:16:32.583
Time flies when I'm with you
It's so unjust when you're away!

00:16:32.666 --> 00:16:36.708
Even the second hand on the clock
Slowed to an hour's pace!

00:16:36.791 --> 00:16:38.750
With you, time melts away

00:16:38.833 --> 00:16:40.875
Without you
Even the dates on the calendar

00:16:40.958 --> 00:16:44.541
Seem to stand still
As if it's been a year

00:16:44.625 --> 00:16:47.875
Oh my love, my love!

00:16:48.333 --> 00:16:52.666
I turned my ship's sail towards you, dear!

00:16:52.750 --> 00:16:56.125
Oh my love, my love!

00:16:56.833 --> 00:17:02.125
I adorned myself
Awaiting your arrival

00:17:18.416 --> 00:17:22.708
I will soar through the skies
And sail through the clouds

00:17:22.791 --> 00:17:26.750
Until I rest in your embrace
I'll be restless

00:17:26.833 --> 00:17:31.000
Adorned in hues so bright
Dazzled by spots

00:17:31.083 --> 00:17:35.041
Until I see you
My eyes cannot sleep

00:17:35.125 --> 00:17:39.333
{\an8}Your words sound like
The waves crashing to me

00:17:39.416 --> 00:17:43.000
This gentle breeze touches me
Like your call

00:17:43.333 --> 00:17:46.791
You totally refrain from eating meat
when he's away for nine months.

00:17:46.875 --> 00:17:48.333
You don't even eat eggs.

00:17:48.583 --> 00:17:52.791
- How do you control your urge?
- I'll eat again when Raju comes back.

00:17:52.875 --> 00:17:54.041
What kind of romance is this?

00:17:54.125 --> 00:17:58.458
Not eating while he's away,
hoisting a flag on the lighthouse…

00:17:58.541 --> 00:17:59.458
What nonsense!

00:17:59.583 --> 00:18:00.791
It's not like that.

00:18:01.791 --> 00:18:04.583
We've seen a lot of regret from childhood.

00:18:06.041 --> 00:18:07.375
While I was away for my studies,

00:18:08.125 --> 00:18:10.000
I used to visit the village
only once every six months.

00:18:11.291 --> 00:18:13.208
He's been away for nine months,
occupied with fishing.

00:18:13.291 --> 00:18:14.708
That's the reason for this romance.

00:18:15.458 --> 00:18:16.375
What is this boss?

00:18:16.541 --> 00:18:18.583
What will I tell my guys
if you pay so less?

00:18:19.875 --> 00:18:21.541
What are you worried about?

00:18:21.750 --> 00:18:22.875
I'll take care of it.

00:18:23.125 --> 00:18:25.375
As soon as I return,
we'll eat only in hotels.

00:18:25.458 --> 00:18:28.208
- What do you talk about for so long?
- We'll dress up nicely.

00:18:28.333 --> 00:18:30.208
- Just hang up and sleep off.
- Buzz off.

00:18:30.291 --> 00:18:31.750
What time will you arrive?

00:18:31.916 --> 00:18:33.416
Eight more hours, dear.

00:18:33.625 --> 00:18:35.750
Raju, just eight more hours!

00:18:36.375 --> 00:18:37.250
I can't wait to see you.

00:18:53.875 --> 00:18:56.375
- Hey, Lachi. Give the bag to Mom.
- Okay, bro.

00:18:56.458 --> 00:18:58.291
- What about the payment?
- I'll distribute it later.

00:18:58.375 --> 00:18:59.625
- What's with him?
- It's love!

00:21:02.125 --> 00:21:05.541
Oh my love, my love!

00:21:06.208 --> 00:21:10.500
I turned my ship sails towards you, dear!

00:21:10.583 --> 00:21:14.208
Oh my love, my love!

00:21:14.416 --> 00:21:18.958
I adorned myself
Awaiting your arrival!

00:21:19.041 --> 00:21:19.875
Hey!

00:21:20.125 --> 00:21:22.541
The three months I spend here
are equal to nine months for me.

00:21:22.958 --> 00:21:24.833
That means each day
counts as three days.

00:21:26.166 --> 00:21:28.541
My God! We shouldn't leave a gap.

00:21:29.750 --> 00:21:30.708
Let's get wild!

00:21:31.708 --> 00:21:32.916
Aunty, leave it.

00:21:33.625 --> 00:21:36.708
I brought hot water.
What are you looking at?

00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:37.875
Give him a bath.

00:21:38.291 --> 00:21:41.708
You wouldn't like it if I did.
Besides, we have plenty of time for that.

00:21:42.125 --> 00:21:43.833
Oh, wow!
What is it?

00:21:44.458 --> 00:21:45.458
Why are you glowing like that?

00:21:46.166 --> 00:21:50.291
It feels like I'm dying
And I swear on you

00:21:50.375 --> 00:21:54.250
When you, in my dreams
Appear before my eyes

00:21:54.333 --> 00:21:58.583
As if there is no difference
Between the earth and the sky

00:21:58.666 --> 00:22:02.583
I could walk among the stars
With you by my side

00:22:02.666 --> 00:22:06.791
Can there be true love
Without any challenges?

00:22:06.875 --> 00:22:08.958
Only after enduring this pain

00:22:09.041 --> 00:22:10.458
We can appreciate the sweetness of love

00:22:10.541 --> 00:22:13.958
{\an8}Oh my dear, my dear!

00:22:14.500 --> 00:22:18.625
I've sailed across oceans for you, dear!

00:22:18.708 --> 00:22:23.083
Oh my dear, my dear!

00:22:23.166 --> 00:22:27.958
{\an8}I've poured all my love for you, dear!

00:22:52.583 --> 00:22:53.583
Hey, Rambabu.

00:22:54.375 --> 00:22:55.625
They're long dead.

00:22:56.041 --> 00:22:58.083
They aren't going anywhere.
Eat slowly.

00:22:58.291 --> 00:22:59.375
Or you might choke.

00:22:59.458 --> 00:23:00.333
Yes, darling.

00:23:01.166 --> 00:23:02.958
You're a big fan of meat, aren't you?

00:23:03.208 --> 00:23:06.041
Why do you vow
to give it up until I return?

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:08.125
I won't from now on.

00:23:08.750 --> 00:23:10.166
I'm unable to stop myself
from eating meat.

00:23:10.625 --> 00:23:11.666
- Have it.
- This is the final time.

00:23:20.083 --> 00:23:22.916
Raju is just like his father, Veerayya.

00:23:24.125 --> 00:23:26.875
He was a leader
to all the fishermen in our village.

00:23:27.458 --> 00:23:30.208
He lived for his people
and also died for them.

00:23:30.625 --> 00:23:33.125
Raju took after his father.

00:23:33.500 --> 00:23:36.833
He believed that if the woman of the house
took charge, the home would thrive.

00:23:36.916 --> 00:23:39.833
He'd hand over every penny
he earned from fishing to the womenfolk.

00:23:41.333 --> 00:23:44.041
He'd stand strong
whenever his team faced challenges.

00:23:49.833 --> 00:23:51.166
- Daddha!
- Give me a quarter.

00:23:53.333 --> 00:23:54.208
Here you go.

00:23:57.791 --> 00:23:58.875
What's wrong with Daddha?

00:24:18.333 --> 00:24:19.208
What's wrong, Daddha?

00:24:21.041 --> 00:24:24.500
They stopped fishing in
our neighboring Munugudu

00:24:25.208 --> 00:24:26.875
and began mining sand instead.

00:24:29.958 --> 00:24:34.291
The contractor gave a bribe
and secured the government's permission.

00:24:37.958 --> 00:24:40.708
- We got the permission to mine here.
- Sir, you know very well

00:24:41.375 --> 00:24:44.166
what happened when you mined sand
where you shouldn't have.

00:24:44.625 --> 00:24:47.166
- The entire vil--
- The entire village drowned.

00:24:47.250 --> 00:24:49.291
You should've taken measures
to save your lives.

00:24:49.708 --> 00:24:51.666
I'll pay compensation when lives are lost.

00:24:52.458 --> 00:24:53.458
Now go away.

00:24:53.791 --> 00:24:55.583
He doesn't care about our lives.

00:24:58.875 --> 00:25:02.875
It feels so humiliating that
I don't want to be called a leader.

00:25:05.583 --> 00:25:09.000
He undermined our dignity.
He dishonored our place.

00:25:10.125 --> 00:25:11.458
After letting go of all of this…

00:25:11.791 --> 00:25:14.875
What do we know?
We don't know anything.

00:25:15.291 --> 00:25:17.625
He even mocked our dialect!

00:25:21.541 --> 00:25:24.666
Your worthless lives,
and your broken accent.

00:25:27.833 --> 00:25:30.041
Even after the entire village
begged him,

00:25:30.791 --> 00:25:33.125
he spoke in a demeaning way
about our profession.

00:25:36.333 --> 00:25:39.125
Get lost!
You losers!

00:25:57.458 --> 00:25:58.625
Guys, come on!

00:27:19.416 --> 00:27:20.250
Dear.

00:27:20.333 --> 00:27:21.791
I'll take care of it, dear.

00:27:27.541 --> 00:27:28.375
Your son?

00:27:30.208 --> 00:27:32.416
The taste of water
changes with the region,

00:27:33.083 --> 00:27:38.250
the smell of soil shifts, the wind,
and even the accent and language.

00:27:40.083 --> 00:27:41.208
That's what defines us.

00:27:43.125 --> 00:27:44.750
They're as pure as a mother's love.

00:27:46.541 --> 00:27:48.833
My father told me this
when I was ten years old.

00:27:50.541 --> 00:27:53.000
He must be over thirty now.

00:27:53.916 --> 00:27:55.416
Doesn't he even know how to say this much?

00:27:57.000 --> 00:27:59.083
If this is how it is with Munugudu…

